{"tid":1265131,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"重温六國論警世名句","createTime":"2019-06-29T04:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:25:36.000Z","uid":182810,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8de1998eeb4366528ed687316db90d36828ea771","tid":1265131,"uid":182810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"1.「秦」以攻取之外，小則獲邑，大則得城，較「秦」之所得，與戰勝而得者，其實百倍；「諸侯」之所亡，與戰敗而亡者，其實亦百倍。則「秦」之所大欲，「諸侯」之所大患，固不在戰矣。思厥先祖父，暴霜露，斬荊棘，以有尺寸之地。<span style=\"color: red;\">子孫視之不甚惜，舉以予人，如棄草芥。今日割五城，明日割十城，然後得一夕安寢。</span>起視四境，<span style=\"color: red;\">而「秦」兵又至矣</span>。然則諸侯之地有限，<span style=\"color: red;\">「暴秦」之欲無厭，奉之彌繁，侵之愈急，故不戰而強弱勝負已判矣。</span><br />\n<br />\n2.悲夫！有如此之勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">而為「秦人」積威所劫，日削月割，以趨於亡。「為國者」，無使為積威之所劫哉！</span><br />\n<br />\n3.夫六國與「秦」皆諸侯，其勢弱於「秦」，而猶有可以不賂而勝之勢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">苟以天下之大而從六國破亡之故事，是又在六國之下矣！</span></span>"},{"pid":"960d1395b119bd05006e4d8a076f57733531cff1","tid":1265131,"uid":182810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:01:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46c88fb9878157d8901c2c51f79392651b023bd8","tid":1265131,"uid":182810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:02:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc829045d11b78545069728b042b99cdc1205ed2","tid":1265131,"uid":182810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:02:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a75e1149e2526654e80d472ce3130c133b4bbdd","tid":1265131,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:12:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8926e8479fa558e4f7af01d1c72eec9ffac3ace8","tid":1265131,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:33:02.000Z","msg":"無能為力"},{"pid":"ef46580234facef096fc27678d39db8d943cada2","tid":1265131,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:49:53.000Z","msg":"而家班中學生個個都要讀六國論唔怪得知咁多00後出嚟"},{"pid":"b681f386ab0a5c343fded55f0a52f74655c2b024","tid":1265131,"uid":258721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:51:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"161ee77f33688001c87cbec30395f0da1957005c","tid":1265131,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:22:44.000Z","msg":"係 7 月1 號 推翻中共 恢復大唐正統 追隨太宗皇帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a1dc822f2c343bd3bd7c352cb9ce9b4e560dc5","tid":1265131,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:25:36.000Z","msg":"仆街<br />\n見到商界都跪低哂<br />\n今鋪係咪玩撚完"}]}